I will package up those Maple files and send them to you.  I have 
begun to use a package called Geomview almost exclusively for all of my
visualization now.  I highly recommend it, as it will render anything 
we need and has simple file formats.  I can give you the ftp site
if you are interested.  Geomview is targeted at SGI's so it takes
full advantage of the graphics capabilities.

